msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 46 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 46 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.44:0.2"
msgid "5. Cakkavattivagga "
msgstr "5. A Wheel Turning Monarch "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn46.44:0.3"
msgid "44. Duppaññasutta "
msgstr "44. Witless "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.100, sc1
msgctxt "sn46.44:1.1"
msgid "Atha kho aññataro bhikkhu yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami … pe … ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then a mendicant went up to the Buddha … and asked him, "

msgctxt "sn46.44:1.2"
msgid "“‘duppañño eḷamūgo, duppañño eḷamūgo’ti, bhante, vuccati. "
msgstr "“Sir, they speak of ‘a witless idiot’. "

msgctxt "sn46.44:1.3"
msgid "Kittāvatā nu kho, bhante, ‘duppañño eḷamūgo’ti vuccatī”ti? "
msgstr "How is a witless idiot defined?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.44:1.4"
msgid "“Sattannaṃ kho, bhikkhu, bojjhaṅgānaṃ abhāvitattā abahulīkatattā ‘duppañño eḷamūgo’ti vuccati. "
msgstr "“Mendicant, they’re called a witless idiot because they haven’t developed and cultivated the seven awakening factors. "

msgctxt "sn46.44:1.5"
msgid "Katamesaṃ sattannaṃ? "
msgstr "What seven? "

msgctxt "sn46.44:1.6"
msgid "Satisambojjhaṅgassa … pe … upekkhāsambojjhaṅgassa—"
msgstr "The awakening factors of mindfulness, investigation of principles, energy, rapture, tranquility, immersion, and equanimity. "

msgctxt "sn46.44:1.7"
msgid "imesaṃ kho, bhikkhu, sattannaṃ bojjhaṅgānaṃ abhāvitattā abahulīkatattā ‘duppañño eḷamūgo’ti vuccatī”ti. "
msgstr "They’re called a witless idiot because they haven’t developed and cultivated these seven awakening factors.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn46.44:1.8"
msgid "Catutthaṃ. "
msgstr ""

